chunks.lyrics: M O U R N I N G B E L O V E T H
A U T U M N A L F I R E S
(/) - Legato Slide (Blank space indicates length of slide)
\ - Slide Down to/Down From (Blank space indicates length of slide)
/ - Slide Up To/Up From (Blank space indicates length of slide)
Riff 1a: Guitar 1 with heavy distortion (Play 4 times)
** These two notes are played on the second and fourth repeats
Riff 1b: Guitar 2 with heavy distortion (Play once through)
* This ghost note is played in place of the 5 note the first time only
On the last repeat, replace the last bar with the supplement:
Riff 5a: Guitar 1 (Play 4 times, replace last bar with supplement after repeats)
Riff 5b: Guitar 2 (Play 4 times, replace last bar with supplement after repeats)
Riff 7a: Guitars 1 and 3 (Play 4 times, guitar 3 is clean) (Tempo = 90 BPM)
Guitar 1's volume is much lower, and the distortion is more of a light "fuzz".
Riff 7c: Guitar 2 (Play once through, fade at end)
